1. A. Develop PHP programs to Use the conditional statements (if-else)

<?php  
$num=55;  
if($num%2==0)
{  
echo "$num is even number";  
}
else
{  
echo "$num is odd number";  
}  
?>

1. B. Develop PHP programs to Use the conditional statements (Switch)

<?php      
    $ch = "B.Sc-IT";  
    switch ($ch)  
    {    
        case "BCA":  
            echo "BCA is 3 years course";  
            break;  
        case "Bsc":  
            echo "Bsc is 3 years course";  
            break;  
        case "B.Tech":  
            echo "B.Tech is 4 years course";  
            break;  
        case "B.Sc-IT":  
            echo "B.Sc-It is 3 years course";  
            break;  
        default:  
            echo "Wrong Choice";  
            break;  
    }  
?>
